Historical_vs_Recent.csv
Description:
This file contains the results of 11 SQL queries comparing older and recent years to identify trends, growth patterns and declining performance areas.

Key metrics included:

Sales volume per year

Average selling price per year

Top makes older vs recent years

Body type demand over the years

Profit margin trend year over year

Regional performance over time (older vs recent)

Average odometer reading over the years

Seller performance over time

Average condition of cars sold over the years

Sales volume by month and quarter

Use this file for: Section 2 of your Looker Studio dashboard (Historical Analysis — Blue charts)
